{"tid":2139743,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"羅湖懲教所有外籍在囚人士計劃挑戰管方　管方已監察","createTime":"2020-08-04T13:07:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-04T14:02:54.000Z","uid":62226,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b9433992fc8bbf244443aea37a6fbac83f291aba","tid":2139743,"uid":62226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T13:07:17.000Z","msg":"懲教署表示，羅湖懲教所早上有59名在囚人士在飯堂早飯期間，其中21名外籍在囚人士不滿奶茶口味，集體要求即時更換，否則拒絕離開飯堂。懲教人員按程序試味，發覺並無不妥。在區域應變隊支援下，懲教人員發出最後警告後，相關在囚人士陸續離開飯堂。現時該21名在囚人士正被隔離調查，署方會密切監察院所情況，並作適當部署。<br />\n<br />\n懲教署表示，羅湖懲教所近日得悉部分外籍在囚人士，計劃在衣食住行各方面挑戰管方，煽動在囚人士情緒，管方監察有關人士，懲教人員會保持高度戒備，防止任何在囚人士利用疫情下的不安情緒，製造事端。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1541829-20200804.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1541829-20200804.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=dUSYmziiyXe0H9uVu%2B4Yd85Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=f1ad3908\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1541829-20200804.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=5a641d5b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1541829-20200804.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"813f5e48e3f78c3699d1a1b53be63a113d1152d7","tid":2139743,"uid":301989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T13:09:05.000Z","msg":"蝻亞之父啲𡃁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"426f889d108956fa90c0d197de68621c75612d38","tid":2139743,"uid":180168,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T13:09:42.000Z","msg":"乜春都煽動"},{"pid":"e0a14b7336517c377120756e6c8ac01851adeb3d","tid":2139743,"uid":1550,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T13:12:00.000Z","msg":"疫情下的不安情緒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b709b4683e7db141bb4e67025d609e5a9d2fa22","tid":2139743,"uid":62226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"r